<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 17:58:06 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a18822a3a735</link><description>&lt;p&gt;查理和泰迪难得的安静时光。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Two brown dogs resting on pet beds and carpet. The upper dog lies on a blue and cream colored bed, and the lower dog rests on the carpet with a whale toy for a pillow." height="4284" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/mihobu/6a18822a3a735.jpg" width="5712"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://mihobu.some.pics"&gt;@mihobu&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 17:58:06 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>今日蓝天</title><link>https://some.pics/6a1875711f41e</link><description>&lt;p&gt;今天的蓝天。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A blue sky and some white clouds above a meadow and a sandy walkway in a park. " height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a1875711f41e.jpg" width="1129"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 17:03:47 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a185dce57e7a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;几年前，我的侄子送了我这朵“乐高”花，当时他大概才5岁。他的理由是，这比真花保存得更久……从那以后我一直把它包着，连枯萎的礼品蝴蝶结都没拆掉。
#FotoVorschlag&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A rose or tulip made of lego in its original wrapping standing on a white surface against a green-grey wall" height="3750" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a185dce57e7a.jpg" width="3000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 15:22:57 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a180ad54eef8</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一只中等体型、毛茸茸的红棕色狗（希腊科科尼犬）戴着红色胸背带，趴在一条土路上，面朝左侧。这只狗位于前景，从侧面拍摄。背景中，空荡荡的小路缓缓向上弯曲，逐渐虚化，两旁是绿树成荫和草坡。

使用Halide Mark III在iPhone 16 Pro上拍摄，并应用瓦伦西亚滤镜进行后期处理。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A medium-sized, fluffy red-brown dog (Greek Kokoni) wearing a red harness lies down on a dirt path, facing to the left. The dog is positioned in the foreground and captured from a side profile view. In the background, the empty path gently curves upward and out of focus, lined with green trees and grassy banks.

Shot with Halide Mark III on an iPhone 16 Pro and edited with the Valencia filter. " height="4032" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/mangochutney/6a180ad54eef8.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://mangochutney.some.pics"&gt;@mangochutney&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 09:29:02 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>森林中的巨石与小径</title><link>https://some.pics/6a1809a940181</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一块巨大的浅灰色圆石醒目地矗立在一条蜿蜒穿过斑驳阳光森林的土路前景中。岩石呈圆形，表面带有纹理和层次。前方的小路延伸向远方，两旁是高挑纤细、绿叶繁茂的树木。温暖的阳光透过树冠洒下，在小路上投下长长的阴影，照亮了森林地表的片片区域。

使用iPhone 16 Pro上的Halide Mark III拍摄，并用Nova滤镜编辑。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A large, light gray boulder sits prominently in the foreground of a dirt path winding through a sun-dappled forest. The rock is rounded with a textured, layered surface. Ahead, the path stretches into the distance, framed by tall, slender trees with green foliage. Warm sunlight filters through the canopy, casting long shadows across the path and illuminating patches of the forest floor.

Captured with Halide Mark III on an iPhone 16 Pro and edited with the Nova filter. " height="1984" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/mangochutney/6a1809a940181.jpg" width="1488"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://mangochutney.some.pics"&gt;@mangochutney&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 09:23:57 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>